results.description:
Important thoughts displayed beautifully on your wall. The right layout can transform the feeling of a space or room. This product arrives precision cut and ready to apply to your wall. Comprehensive application instructions are included. A 30-day satisfaction guarantee is also included for your peace of mind. Order this stunning layout today! At Words Anywhere we're as busy as bees turning over our vinyl inventory! We produce new vinyl lettering daily, and order fresh vinyl monthly. Just like anything, vinyl has a shelf-life. Some vinyl sellers make 100 copies of a layout, put them on a shelf, then sell them cheap. The customer thinks, "What a deal!", but the problem is those layouts can sit on the shelf for months or years, moving beyond the product's shelf-life. What you receive may be more brittle and less tacky because it's old vinyl; it's more difficult to install and has uncertain longevity. The best burger places don't start cooking your burger until after you've ordered, and the best vinyl places don't produce your layout until after you've ordered (and from fresh vinyl stock!) That's the Words Anywhere way.

*** If you'd like to order this layout in a size or color not specified, please add a comment at checkout. There's no difference in cost for a color change. The only added cost to you would be if you wanted a bigger size, and then only in proportion to the size increase.

results.description:
Live Laugh Love Bracelet, Memory Wire Bracelet, Wrap Bracelet, Seed Bead Bracelet, Beaded Bracelet, Inspirational Jewelry, Colorful Bracelet

This memory wire bracelet is made with five rows of colorful, high quality glass seed beads in coordinating colors with rows of various glass beads in bright red, yellow, orange and lime green colors. Bright silver plated accent beads are spaced throughout the bracelet and all are strung onto silver plated memory wire. At one end of the bracelet is a silver plated charm with the quote "Live Love Laugh" and at the other end is a Czech glass beaded drop. Very pretty and easy to wear but also a way to motivate and inspire yourself and others whenever you wear it!

Memory wire maintains its shape, no matter how it is twisted or stretched. Instead of using a clasp, you wind it onto your wrist, making it easy to fit any wrist shape and almost any sized wrist. No more guessing if it will fit or trying to fuss with a clasp when putting it on or taking it off! This wrap bracelet makes an excellent gift and can be stacked with other bracelets for a completely unique look.

This bracelet will ship securely packaged inside a cotton-lined kraft box ready to wear or gift to someone special!

Happy Rocks add fun and whimsy to your decor - boldly displayed on a coffee table or bookshelf or windowsill; more subtly displayed in nooks and crannies and corners; and around your plants and meditation altar. Happy Rocks are the perfect one-of-a-kind gift. Thinner/flatter rocks often do well on an easel. Smaller rocks - pocket rocks - can be carried with you to offer comfort, positive energy and good vibes everywhere you go. Interested in a custom rock? Message me!

This Happy Rock measures approximately 3 1/4" x 2 1/8".

All rocks are sprayed with clear Rustoleum lacquer.
